videos.description: Ohio State gets the steal and Jae'Sean Tate with the nice bounce to Kam Williams for the layup.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Ohio State early

videos.description: Melo Trimble finds Jared Nickens who drains the 3-pointer while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Maryland's Nickens gets the 3-pointer plus the foul

videos.description: Maryland coach Mark Turgeon explains how Melo Trimble ran the offense for the Terps in the first half.
videos.headline: Maryland's coach Mark Turgeon talks about Trimble and his teams offense

videos.description: During a timeout, Ohio State coach Thad Matta loses his gum while talking to his players, however he manages to catch it with his hand before placing it back into his mouth.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Matta can coach and chew gum at same time) 2017/01/31

videos.headline: Matta can coach and chew gum at same time

videos.description: Jae'Sean Tate keeps the ball after being trapped and gets the layin plus the foul for Ohio State.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Tate keeps the ball for himself and gets the lay in

videos.description: Melo Trimble with the quick first step and then gets the nice up-and-under layin to go.
videos.headline: Trimble with the nice up-and-under layin

videos.description: Damonte Dodd gets the block and goes out running,  finding Kevin Huerter for the dunk.
videos.headline: Big block by Maryland's Dodd leads to fastbreak dunk

videos.description: Maryland's Melo Trimble talks about his play down the stretch and how the Terps were able to defeat Ohio State.
videos.headline: Trimble talks about his mentality down the stretch in win over Ohio State

videos.description: Maryland gets a win over Ohio State thanks to Justin Jackson strong performance.
videos.headline: Breaking down Justin Jackson's strong game in 77-71 win over Ohio State
